    dc:description "Fig. 2. – A–B: Stenus (Nestus) raddei Ryvkin, 1987: ♂ (Russia: Magadan Area: Sibit-Tyhellakh). A. Aedeagus, ventral view. B. Apical part of aedeagus, ventral view. – C–D: S. (N.) illotulus Puthz, 1972: ♂ (Russia: Amur Area: Zeyskiy Nature Reserve). C. Aedeagus, ventral view. D. Apical part of aedeagus, ventral view. Right paramere removed. – E. S. (N.) confusus J. Sahlberg, 1876: ♂ (Russia: Kalinin Area: Putilovo). Aedeagus, ventral view. – Scales = 0.1 mm." ;
